{"ts":"2026-05-30T21:48:12.551Z","author":"codex","op":"update","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-30T21:48:12.551Z"},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/description","value":"User decision (2026-05-30): pm-web stays published scoped as @unbrained/pm-web. A prior audit agent (commit ae4f607) had flipped package.json name to unscoped pm-web to match the pm- branding convention, but never claimed/published the unscoped name on npm (still E404) — which would have caused publish 404s. @unbrained/pm-web@2026.5.29-1 is already published and working; pm install github.com/unbraind/pm-web is unaffected by the npm scope. Reverted name back to @unbrained/pm-web. This is the one intentional scope exception in the otherwise-unscoped pm- ecosystem."}],"before_hash":"74759585bf1396bc403ff88bf493ba998321254e60a9ba75dc8b32ccf2871cef","after_hash":"90177d91df0ca7feb8e40498968456be3eac793250624135cdee080ffa0c9529"}
